By":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"聯署傳送門<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdcouiLgT9PJxUL1qzhwBFYUsaoj61s0tHqOTE_qJxOZGlCZQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdcouiLgT9PJxUL1qzhwBFYUsaoj61s0tHqOTE_qJxOZGlCZQ%2Fviewform&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B063eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=fdb04111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdcouiLgT9PJxUL1qzhwBFYUsaoj61s0tHqOTE_qJxOZGlCZQ/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"03c2325a6a97637bdcbe9d7b56a95315a6b91e33","tid":2424116,"uid":321895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:24:59.000Z","msg":"粗言辱罵保安兩名中大學生被記過並須完成義務工作<br />\n<br />\n中大表示，早前有兩名學生被投訴不遵守校園出入管理措施，並以粗言穢語辱罵他人，兩人分別被記過。<br />\n<br />\n中大表示，一名學生於去年12月10日進入大學校園時，拒絕出示學生證及以粗言穢語辱罵保安人員，並於1月12日在校園再次以粗言穢語辱罵保安人員，事件經所屬書院紀律委員會詳細審議後，相關學生被記過二次，並須於畢業前完成30小時義務工作。<br />\n<br />\n另一名學生於去年12月11日，以手機網上直播與大學保安人員理論期間 ，多次以粗言穢語辱罵保安人員，所屬書院紀律委員會裁定學生記過一次，並須於畢業前完成20小時義務工作。<br />\n<br />\n按照中大《全日制本科生總學則》，記過三次的學生將被開除學籍。<br />\n<br />\n校方指出，兩名學生的違規行為性質嚴重及有損大學校譽，兩人被處分外，均已撰寫道歉信，向受影響的員工道歉。"},{"pid":"b7aa15f35836cb6239a338bb9d2929967235618a","tid":2424116,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:25:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b9300651fb1d5481664cf0c9285d86cde90f6c39","tid":2424116,"uid":321895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"唔show證 = 記過2次<br />\n<br />\n扮仆街 = 收道歉信<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c3d200eb19544eea5bd55c389e0b5d2426c6b1","tid":2424116,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:26:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"eb37dff0ffe4399e72223d9ae5d520c2f68cfaa5","tid":2424116,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:27:20.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a7e8f0c09e7593209999277ac58f547ee42f0b2b","tid":2424116,"uid":321